data.value:
The source code of this program can be found on GitHub.
- This project can be opened on Visual Studio 2012 and newer, without the need of conversion - The .NET Framework 4.8 Developer Pack must be installed to open this project
Do you want to suggest a new feature to be included in a future version? Have you experienced a bug you want to report? Don't hesitate on reporting feedback or (even better) contributing (you'll need a GitHub account). Your feedback is critical.
Do you want to enjoy the latest features? Check the Hummingbird branch! Weekly updates, new features and a sneak peek of the program's future
